{"id": "1398121135845146825", "channel_id": "1398121135845146825", "type": 0, "author_id": "583094634939678743", "author_name": "taokonn", "author_bot": false, "content": "Hello! Very new to the game! I was drawn to the art so really looking forward to getting into this~ I already read Flare’s doc but I still dont have a lot of the units in sample teams. Would love suggestions please~ \n\nCurrently I have been using Tawil as my dps and Caecus/Goliath/Tulu, but maybe I don’t have enough dupes yet? It doesn’t always feel smooth to play and I’m stuck around chapter 5 right now. \n\n(I would love if i could hse Doresain/Helot Catena along with Tawil but I assume hard to lol. Maybe for d tide but I dont have enough units to try yet I guess)\n\nWelcome your recommendations! ☺️", "timestamp": "2025-07-25T01:54:14.620000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2025-07-25T01:58:25.095000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1398121136159588404", "filename": "IMG_2105.jpeg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 743181, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1398121135845146825/1398121136159588404/IMG_2105.jpeg?ex=69cd2386&is=69cbd206&hm=6c8735f6ebe2431843d71b5ff2533ad8f28884c4597cb96b66358ab0c40617aa&"}, {"id": "1398121136960573461", "filename": "IMG_2106.jpeg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 719319, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1398121135845146825/1398121136960573461/IMG_2106.jpeg?ex=69cd2386&is=69cbd206&hm=5853a1792581b75d7f8653e0b272fb5aadde1852278b1039054081f4bc14555e&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1398121135845146825", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "Team comp help", "forum_channel_id": "1356200968311803956"}
{"id": "1398125445232201758", "channel_id": "1398121135845146825", "type": 0, "author_id": "693905974750216212", "author_name": "fishhazardthewizard", "author_bot": false, "content": "You might want more dupes for the ones you currently are using if you plan to go forward with them, yes\n\nFor using doresain earlygame, he works alright with tawil, but she’ll probably take on more of a support/secondary role, and you’ll want either leigh or agrippa (the latter is better) in lieu of thais for embryo generation!", "timestamp": "2025-07-25T02:11:22.058000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1398121135845146825", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "Team comp help", "forum_channel_id": "1356200968311803956"}
